      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Whirlwind of a Stage",
        "Client": "Eccentric Writer",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve been suffering from a severe\r\ncase of writer\u0027s block, so I asked\r\nan acquaintance of mine to set up\r\na grand stage performance. All you\r\nhave to do, Hunter, is play your part,\r\nand surely I will find the inspiration\r\nI need to finish my romance novel!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Mise en sc\u00E8ne incroyable",
        "Client": "\u00C9crivaine excentrique",
        "Description": "Je n\u0027ai plus d\u0027id\u00E9es, c\u0027est\r\nofficiel ! C\u0027est pour \u00E7a que j\u0027ai\r\ndemand\u00E9 \u00E0 une connaissance de\r\npr\u00E9parer un spectacle. Si tu\r\njoues ton r\u00F4le, je trouverai\r\nl\u0027inspiration dont j\u0027ai besoin\r\npour finir mon roman !",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Uno spettacolo tumultuoso",
        "Client": "Scrittrice eccentrica",
        "Description": "Ho il blocco dello scrittore,\r\nquindi ho chiesto a un amico\r\ndi organizzare un grande\r\nspettacolo. Devi solo recitare\r\nla tua parte e io trover\u00F2\r\nsicuramente l\u0027ispirazione per\r\nfinire il mio romanzo rosa.",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "B\u00FChne frei!",
        "Client": "Exzentrische Autorin",
        "Description": "Ich leide an einer ganz hartn\u00E4ckigen\r\nSchreibblockade, also habe ich eine\r\nBekannte gebeten, ein gro\u00DFes Schau-\r\nspiel vorzubereiten. Du musst nur\r\ndeine Rolle spielen, dann finde ich\r\nschon die n\u00F6tige Inspiration f\u00FCr das\r\nEnde meines Liebesromans!",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Torbellino en el escenario",
        "Client": "Escritora exc\u00E9ntrica",
        "Description": "\u00A1Me he quedado oficialmente\r\nsin ideas! As\u00ED que he pedido a\r\nun amigo que me ayude a\r\norquestar una gran obra.\r\n\u00A1Cumple tu cometido y hallar\u00E9\r\nla inspiraci\u00F3n para acabar mi\r\nnovela rom\u00E1ntica!",
